======================================================================

python-xsdata (Naive XML bindings for python)

xsData is a complete data binding library for python allowing
developers to access and use XML and JSON documents as simple
python objects rather than using DOM.

HOME: https://xsdata.readthedocs.io/

======================================================================
REQUIRES: python-click-default-group python-toposort python-typing-extensions 

